data.meta_description: Sanyu: With Abby Mukiibi Nkaaga, Marion Asilo, Blessing Naturinda, Timothy Lwanga. This tells the story of an innocent, rural teenage girl that is forced to leave her family and her pursuit for education to do a maid's job for a complex, wealthy urban family. It is here where she falls for the young son of her employer.
